punto-switcher (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Fcitx5 module for automatic ru<->en keyboard layout correction on Wayland.
  * Features: auto-switch, swap-last-word, swap-selection, Qt6 config GUI.

